32. Database Governance Rules

DB-001

Every table must contain tenant_id.

DB-002

All deletes are soft deletes.

DB-003

Financial records immutable.

DB-004

Audit logs append only.

DB-005

All financial amounts use DECIMAL.

DB-006

UUID primary keys everywhere.

DB-007

Every write operation audited.

DB-008

No cross-tenant joins allowed.

